rows.label: qst104710_msg001
rows.name:
You've arrived as well. The
refugees went to the camp set
up in the garrison. Let's go too.

rows.label: qst104710_msg101
rows.name:
There might be trouble at the upcoming
meeting between the people of Torigo
and the refugees at the consulate.

rows.label: qst104710_msg102
rows.name: I want you to join as bodyguards.

rows.label: qst104710_msg201
rows.name:
We will guard the inside
of the consulate.

rows.label: qst104710_msg0001
rows.name:
I wonder if Father and
Enju-chan are okay...

rows.label: qst104710_msg0101
rows.name:
Father and the others are
okay? Thank goodness!
